<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,minimum-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no" />
		<title>底部灰色框</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/reset.css"/>
		<script src="js/jquery-2.2.4.min.js" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>
		<style type="text/css">
			.btm-prompt{
				width: 100%;
				height: 180px;
				background: url(img/btm-bg-grid.png) 0 0 no-repeat;
				background-size: 100% 100%;
				max-width: 750px;
				min-width: 320px;
				position: fixed;
				bottom: 0;
				z-index: 9;
			}
			.btm-prompt p{
				font-size: 16px;
				color: white;
				text-align: center;
				line-height: 28px;
			}
			.btm-prompt .p1{
				padding-top: 10px;
			}
			.btm-prompt .grid-delete{
				display: block;
				position: absolute;
				top: 10px;
				right: 10px;
				width: 20px;
				height: 20px;	
			}
			.btm-prompt .grid-delete img{
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="btm-prompt">
			<p class="p1">温馨提示：您还未设置登录密码</p>
			<p> 建议您设置登录密码，以便电脑端登陆。</p>
			<span class="grid-delete"><img src="img/grid-delete.png"/></span>
		</div>
		<script type="text/javascript">
			$('.btm-prompt .grid-delete').click(function(){
				$('.btm-prompt').hide();
			});
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
